<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="40" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,649,1141]" pageId="9" pageNumber="40">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,313,1045,1069]" pageId="9" pageNumber="40">Remarks.</emphasis>
Based on the aedeagus characters of the 
<typeStatus box="[782,883,1045,1069]" pageId="9" pageNumber="40">holotype</typeStatus>
, we follow 
<bibRefCitation author="Dworakowska" box="[1017,1261,1045,1069]" pageId="9" pageNumber="40" refString="Dworakowska, I. (1997) A review of the genus Alebroides Matsumura, with description of Shumka gen. nov. (Homoptera: Auchenorrhyncha: Cicadellidae). Oriental Insects, 31, 241 - 407." type="journal article" year="1997">
Dworakowska (
<number box="[1195,1253,1045,1069]" pageId="9" pageNumber="40" value="1997.0">1997</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
in placing 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Alebroides" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="discretus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="40">Alebroides discretus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the 
<taxonomicName box="[423,573,1081,1105]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Alebroides" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hachijonis">
<emphasis box="[423,573,1081,1105]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="40">A. hachijonis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group rather than the 
<taxonomicName box="[917,1076,1081,1105]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Alebroides" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="marginatus">
<emphasis box="[917,1076,1081,1105]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="40">A. marginatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group. The aedeagus is re-illustrated in 
<figureCitation box="[330,458,1117,1141]" captionStart="FIGURES 42 – 50. 42, 43" captionStartId="10.[151,264,1931,1954]" captionTargetBox="[167,1425,743,1871]" captionTargetId="figure@10.[151,1436,709,1910]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURES 42 – 50. 42, 43, Alebroides discretus Chou &amp; Zhang (paratype); 44, 45, Alebroides qinlinganus Chou &amp; Zhang (holotype); 46 – 50, Alebroides shaanxiensis Chou &amp; Zhang (holotype). 42, 44, 46, aedeagus, lateral view; 43, 45, 47, aedeagus, ventral view; 48, pygofer and anal tube process, lateral view; 49, ventral pygofer appendage; 50, anal tube process." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/203611/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="40">
Figs 
<number box="[385,458,1117,1141]" pageId="9" pageNumber="40" value="42.43">42, 43</number>
</figureCitation>
.
</paragraph>
